                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-11-defend205 t18301209-11-punish64"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 19.</p>
               <p>COTTON - <rs id="t18301209-11-verdict65" type="verdictDescription">
